<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kerryn Darkwater</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-04 14:00:32</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My first statement says it all. Im a paladin.<BR>
<BR>
I have a base INT of 75 and its unbuffed. Ive never bought any item that had it simply because it never came with a stat I could justify.<BR>
<BR>
Let me tell you that 13 WIS for me justifys 13 INT.<BR>
<BR>
As a Paladin Im two things. Im a warrior and AC rules. And Im a cleric too and I need mana. Any Paladin who doesnt want mana should go be a warrior and duel wield.<BR>
<BR>
This is at least one more spell in a fight and if that spell is G Heal I just saved the wizards life. The cleric may be out of mana and we win the fight.<BR>
<BR>
Why I even bother because all through the fights hes whining that I have a 13 INT neckpiece and the clerics moaning that he would love the 13 WIS and the 7 AC.<BR>
<BR>
Go figure it.</font></td></tr></table>
